snippet.title: 19 LINE [Trailer] - A Horror Visual Novel
snippet.description:
19 Line is a horror visual novel made by Nico Saraintaris, Octavio Saraintaris & MakeRenders (Augusto Saraintaris + Francisco Araujo)
https://nicosaraintaris.itch.io/19-line

- Press Kit
bit.ly/19Line_Presskit

- Features
 • Branching narrative with seven multiple endings.
 • Dark and gripping storytelling.
 • Gorgeous art by MakeRenders (https://www.instagram.com/makerenders/)
 • Original OST.

- Platforms
 • Windows
 • Mac

- Release Date
August 10.
